        "Title": "The Rat",
        "Description": "Hello 47,\rWelcome to Chongqing.\r\rYour targets are three prominent members of Hush&apos;s team:\r- Fengge Fang\r- Shihong Luo\r- Shirong Dai\r\rThe trio conducted a series of illegal experiments on humans to further their own research, but to no avail. They eventually joined Hush&apos;s team to hide from justice. Until now!\r\rGood Luck!\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Druid Forest.\r\rFC72",
